page.title: 02Sutton on Seas Countryside.
page.content: In the countryside there are a lot of fields,dykes and lanes off the main road.If you went out in the morning you would see a lot of wild life.In the Autumn there is a lot of blossom on the trees.There are a lot of farm animals round in the fields.There are many fields round the countryside where there are crops growing. Most of the land has streams running into dykes and drains.The countryside has a lot of wild life which includes foxes,hares,rats, stoats and partridges. You cannot see most of the animals.Lots are seen running across the fields and along the roads.Some of them get run run over by vehicles.Some of the farmers leave mud on the road after they have been in the fields.
